reviews.review_text: OUT F'n STANDING THIS SOUNDS AMAZING.....GREAT WORK!!!!
Go to Heaven Show Fun Fact:  The 7 "Go to Heaven" songs played may be due, in part, to the fact that the album was released three days before this show.  Very well played and good sound quality.

A Sun Rise on the Beaches of Paradise.. ...Is how I feel when I listen to this Estimated. Jerry's solo is like being up early on a beach and watching the sun rise. 

I also love when they revert back to Estimated after the jam, only one of three attempts as a band. 

Great sounding tape as well.
